description: My first money earned online! This has proven me that earning money online is easier than I thought and I can actually do it!.
What started as a test product actually earned me decent money! It was time to refocus on something else tho.
First month for what I originaly called Launch Kit Studio. Earned by making logo kits for small creators
Making logo kits and designing on the side of my day job.
I finally quit my day job and went full in on Launch Studio!
Landed some great clients for Launch Studio! Continuing the grind and focusing more on client aquisition.
After some rough days I got back on track. Landed a huge colab with a development agency.
Things seem to be really taking off, making connections with others is the best thing you can do for your business
Working on stabilizing my revenue and income of clients. Improved my studio branding.
